/pt/l/w/iui_heroku_com/iui/README

I use this project to demo how to create a simple iphone webapp using rails to serve iui CSS and javascript from heroku.

I use these steps to deploy this code on heroku:

- cd ~
- git clone git@github.com:bikle/iui-4-heroku.git iui4heroku
- cd iui4heroku
- If your name is Bob and you have a Heroku account, run this command:
- heroku apps:create iui4bob
- git push heroku master
- point your iPhone at http://iui4bob.heroku.com

If you have questions, e-me:
dan@bot4.us

